Revision history for Perl extension Device::Modbus

0.023 23 march 2018
    - Found bug in the server code for Read/Write Holding Registers requests,
      code 0x17. The registers being read were those that were just written.

0.022 2017-08-16
    - Client croaks when it builds a request with missing or incorrect
      parameters. It refuses to send exception objects to the remote
      device, as opposed to previous versions. 

0.01  14 juillet 2015
	- original version
